CERTIFICATE
United States of America Western District of Washington
ss.
I, JAMES C. DRAKE, Clerk of the Circuit Court of the United States, for the Western District of Washington, do hereby certify that the foregoing attached papers constitute the JUDGMENT ROLL in the foregoing entitled cause, No 776 wherein In re: Application of S. A. Sylvester for a Writ of Habeas Corpus Plaintiff
In Testimony Whereof, I have hereunto set my hand and affixed the Seal of said Circuit Court, this the 30 day of Dec A. D. 1911
JAMES C. DRAKE, Clerk.
By B O Wregler Deputy Clerk.
